text:
Oh, you're up early.
The lesson starts in 30 minutes... Wait, are you cleaning?

If there's a mess,
I can take care of it, you know?

Oh, it's not that...!
The room was clean!

But, we always use
the lesson room.
So this cleaning is just to show my appreciation!

T-Thanks are unnecessary...!
It's just something Amana does on her own...!
